title.narrative: WHOLE OF SYRIA RESPONSE: GAZIANTEP HUB

description.narrative: Effective Implementation of whole of Syria Approach from Gaziantep, which contributes to Child Health, Child Protection And Emergencies, Education In Emergencies, Equitable Access To Quality Education, Health And Emergencies, Nutrition And Emergencies, Prevention And Response Services For Violence Against Children, Sanitation, Wash And Emergencies. UNICEF aims to achieve this through Systems Strengthening And Institution Building. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: GRP1: Governments and regional institutions in MENA benefit from UNICEF technical and other support to achieve sustainable results for children and adolescents in development and humanitarian contexts.
